  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Shogi game!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/4f1c1e6750d1f43b2a4c629d38cddbe3.avif?t=1772361450\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shogi 3D is a faithful take on the famous Japanese board game. Take a sip of coffee and enjoy a relaxing experience, playing strategic matches with traditional rules in a serene Japanese temple.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/ebdc014fd324ab9ca6b7252953662697.poster.avif?t=1772361450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/ebdc014fd324ab9ca6b7252953662697.webm?t=1772361450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/ebdc014fd324ab9ca6b7252953662697.mp4?t=1772361450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Shogi 3D</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shogi 3D faithfully recreates the classic Japanese board game with a relaxing 3D experience. Enjoy the depth of strategic gameplay and traditional rules, perfect for both newcomers and experienced players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/2ab30bd7a3e972793fa135191250b9be.poster.avif?t=1772361450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/2ab30bd7a3e972793fa135191250b9be.webm?t=1772361450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368350/extras/2ab30bd7a3e972793fa135191250b9be.mp4?t=1772361450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in a tranquil Japanese temple-inspired environment, Shogi 3D offers a peaceful atmosphere for strategic matches. Challenge friends or other players while enjoying the serene surroundings and immersive gameplay.</p>",
